[bash] cd /etc/yum.repos.d/

curl -O http://download.opensuse.org/repositories/security://shibboleth/CentOS%5C_5/security:shibboleth.repo[1]

yum install shibboleth.i386 [/bash]

Press y 3 times. Done. Proceed to configuration..[2]

